dcterms:description: The trip records dataset used in the experiments is from New York City Taxi Records in January 2011. Here we select the trips whose pickup and dropoff location are both in Manhattan Island.
dcterms:title: New York City Taxi Records

dcterms:description: The road graph of Manhattan Island is constructed from various types of ways (primary, primary_link, secondary, tertiary, residential, unclassified, road and living street) to build the road graph.
dcterms:title: Road Graph of Manhattan Island
